OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister has condemned a
OL,7,Fseries of "abhorrent" attacks on the
OL,8,FJewish community in north London.
OL,10,FSir Keir Starmer vowed that those
OL,11,Fresponsible would be "found and
OL,12,Fbrought to justice", in a post on the
OL,13,Fsocial media platform X.
OL,15,FIt follows the alleged "firebombing"
OL,16,Fof a synagogue in Harrow, which the
OL,17,FMetropolitan Police says happened at
OL,18,Faround midnight on Sunday, April 19.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FCounter-terrorism officers are now
OL,7,Finvestigating the attack and treating
OL,8,Fit as arson.
OL,10,FThe incident is the latest in a series
OL,11,Fof similar attacks, with others
OL,12,Frecently reported in Finchley, Golders
OL,13,FGreen and Hendon.
OL,15,FChief Rabbi Sir Ephraim Mirvis called
OL,16,Fit "a cowardly arson attack" and
OL,17,Fwarned "a sustained campaign of
OL,18,Fviolence and intimidation against the
OL,19,FJewish community of the UK is
OL,20,Fgathering momentum".
OL,26,@xD@DOUxD@\O]yD@HOU|D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FThe full post from the PM said: "I am
OL,7,Fappalled by recent attempted
OL,8,Fantisemitic arson attacks in North
OL,9,FLondon.
OL,11,F"This is abhorrent and it will not be
OL,12,Ftolerated. Attacks on our Jewish
OL,13,Fcommunity are attacks on Britain.
OL,15,F"We are increasing visible policing
OL,16,Fand those responsible will be found
OL,17,Fand brought to justice. We will not
OL,18,Frest in the pursuit of perpetrators."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FCharities and London's mayor Sadiq
OL,7,FKhan have also condemned the
OL,8,Fperpetrators, while the rabbi of
OL,9,FKenton United Synagogue today preached
OL,10,Fa message of solidarity.
OL,12,FBottle had been 'thrown through window'
OL,14,FIn a statement, the Metropolitan
OL,15,FPolice said: "At around midnight on
OL,16,FSunday, 19 April officers on
OL,17,Fdeterrence and reassurance patrols
OL,18,Ffollowing a series of incidents in
OL,19,Fnorth west London noticed damage to a
OL,20,Fwindow of the Kenton United Synagogue
OL,21,Fin Shaftesbury Avenue, Harrow.
OL,26,@wD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,F"On further inspection they saw smoke
OL,7,Finside a room and evidence that a
OL,8,Fbottle with some sort of accelerant
OL,9,Fhad been thrown through the window.
OL,11,F"The London Fire Brigade was called
OL,12,Fand firefighters searched the building
OL,13,Fto confirm that there was no further
OL,14,Ffire risk.
OL,16,F"The incident is being treated as
OL,17,Farson and an investigation is underway
OL,18,Fled by Counter Terrorism Policing
OL,19,FLondon, supported by local officers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUxD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
