OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,F'We will not be deterred' - Rabbi
OL,7,FYehuda Black
OL,9,FThis morning, prayers went ahead for
OL,10,Fthe community at Kenton United
OL,11,FSynagogue and were held in the rabbi's
OL,12,Fhome.
OL,14,FSpeaking to the minyan (a quorum of
OL,15,Fmembers needed for prayer) Rabbi
OL,16,FYehuda Black said: "When I woke up
OL,17,Fthis morning, I thought 'I will go and
OL,18,Fminyan somewhere else', but my wife
OL,19,Fsaid to me - 'we must stand together
OL,20,Fand we must make a minyan in our
OL,21,Fhouse'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,F"This is what I think we as Jews
OL,7,Fshould be doing. We must not be
OL,8,Fdeterred by what is taking place out
OL,9,Fthere.
OL,11,F"It must not in any way affect who we
OL,12,Fare as Jews. We come together and we
OL,13,Fdaven (pray) together. We pray and we
OL,14,Fstudy the Torah together, and this
OL,15,Fallows us to continue."
OL,17,FA spokesperson for United Synagogue, a
OL,18,Fcharity supporting the religious
OL,19,Fcentre in Harrow, said they were
OL,20,F"deeply saddened" by the attacks on
OL,21,FJewish venues.
OL,26,@uD@GpmuD@Lpn
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FThey added: "A synagogue is not just a
OL,7,Fbuilding, it is a place of worship,
OL,8,Fcommunity and ` theoretically ` safety.
OL,10,F"To target it in this way is a deeply
OL,11,Fdisturbing act that strikes at the
OL,12,Fheart of Jewish life.
OL,14,F"Thank God no one was hurt and we are
OL,15,Fgrateful to the emergency services and
OL,16,FCommunity Security Trust for their
OL,17,Fswift response today."
OL,26,@nD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FPaul Taylor, president of the charity,
OL,7,Fadded: "The Prime Minister should
OL,8,Fdeclare publicly what the Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunity has known for some time:
OL,10,Fthis is an epidemic of anti-Jewish
OL,11,Fhate."
OL,13,FMeanwhile, chief communications
OL,14,Fofficer Richard Verber told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation: "Whilst most British Jews
OL,16,Fdon't want to be thinking about 'where
OL,17,Felse am I going to live if Britain is
OL,18,Fnot safe?', that is a conversation
OL,19,Fthat is certainly now beginning to
OL,20,Fhappen."
OL,26,@oD@HOUwD@NOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
