CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FHe was asked if there had been
OL,7,Fdiscussions at the synagogue about
OL,8,Fsecurity concerns given the attacks in
OL,9,Fthe past weeks.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's a tragic answer that
OL,12,FI'm going to give you... these
OL,13,Fconversations have been happening not
OL,14,Ffor days or weeks or months, but for
OL,15,Fyears.
OL,26,@sD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,F"I don't know if you've ever had the
OL,7,Fopportunity to visit a Jewish school
OL,8,For a synagogue but it can sometimes
OL,9,Ffeel there's less security getting
OL,10,Finto a prison in the UK, the amount of
OL,11,Fsecurity guards, cameras, barbed wire.
OL,13,F"It's completely not right that in
OL,14,F2026 the British Jewish community has
OL,15,Fto live like this, these are not new
OL,16,Fconversations that the community has
OL,17,Fhad to have, but... these have been
OL,18,Framped up in the past few weeks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FMr Verber said the community has been
OL,7,F"very grateful" for the emergency
OL,8,Fservices and Government's responses
OL,9,Ffollowing "horrific attacks" such as
OL,10,Fthe Heaton Park, Manchester, terror
OL,11,Fattack and the torching of four Jewish
OL,12,Fcommunity ambulances in Golders Green,
OL,13,Fnorth-west London, last month.
OL,15,F"But the question is, what can the
OL,16,FGovernment now do to prevent these
OL,17,Fattacks happening? It's good and we
OL,18,Fare grateful for the response
OL,19,Fafterwards, but nobody wants these
OL,20,Fattacks to happen", he said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@OO]qD@KOUqD@\O]wD@AOU|D@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FMr Taylor likewise emphasised the need
OL,7,Ffor prevention.
OL,9,F"The Government and local police
OL,10,Fforces have responded well to the
OL,11,Frecent appalling attacks including
OL,12,FHeaton Park Hebrew Congregation and
OL,13,FHatzola ambulances, but it is clear
OL,14,Fthat more must be done to prevent
OL,15,Fthese attacks occurring at all", Mr
OL,16,FTaylor said.
OL,18,FPhil Rosenberg, president of the Board
OL,19,Fof Deputies of British Jews, said the
OL,20,Fnews was "deeply concerning".
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
