SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FHe added: "I think we need to over the
OL,7,Fcoming days be speaking to government
OL,8,Fabout how we take a very firm line on
OL,9,Fthe spreaders of hate, whether that is
OL,10,Fgroups, extremist groups advocating
OL,11,Ffor this, working out who this group
OL,12,Fthat keeps claiming responsibility and
OL,13,Fshowing videos of these attacks is and
OL,14,Fgetting behind that."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
