PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776636668
OL,3,CPrime Minister condemns 'abhorrent'
OL,4,Carson attacks on Jewish venues
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Community
OL,7,FSecurity Trust, the charity which
OL,8,Fmonitors antisemitism and provides
OL,9,Fprotection for Jewish communities in
OL,10,Fthe UK, said: "We want to thank the
OL,11,FMet Police and London Fire Brigade for
OL,12,Fresponding quickly and for all they
OL,13,Fare doing to protect the Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunity during this unprecedented
OL,15,Fperiod.
OL,17,F"We are supporting the affected
OL,18,Flocation and are working closely with
OL,19,Fthe police as they investigate and
OL,20,Fseek to identify those responsible."
OL,26,@rD@OOUyD@AOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
